QuestionText: "// int初期値\nint[] a = new int[1];\nSystem.out.println(a[0]); // ____"
"// double初期値\ndouble[] d = new double[1];\nSystem.out.println(d[0]); // ____"
"// boolean初期値\nboolean[] b = new boolean[1];\nSystem.out.println(b[0]); // ____"
"// String初期値\nString[] s = new String[1];\nSystem.out.println(s[0]); // ____"
"// char初期値\nchar[] c = new char[1];\n// c[0] はヌル文字？"
"// 文字列化\nint[] a = {1};\nSystem.out.println(Arrays.toString(a)); // ____"
"// var型推論\nvar a = new int[]{1};\n// aの型は？"
"// Object代入\nObject obj = new int[]{1};\n// 可能？"
"// short初期値\nshort[] s = new short[1];\nSystem.out.println(s[0]); // ____"
"// long初期値\nlong[] l = new long[1];\nSystem.out.println(l[0]); // ____"
